	* configure.ac: Fix NATIVE conditional.
	* Makefile.in, configure: Regenerate.

--- a/src/gotools/Makefile.am
+++ b/src/gotools/Makefile.am
@@ -33,7 +33,7 @@
 # Use the compiler we just built.
